          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-947B14H1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">Y</hi>OU always are making a God of your spouse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B14H1-line-2" n="2">But this neither reason nor conscience allows;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B14H1-line-3" n="3">Perhaps you will say, 'tis in gratitude due,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B14H1-line-4" n="4">And you adore him, because he adores you.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B14H1-line-5" n="5">Your argument's weak, and so you will find,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-947B14H1-line-6" n="6">For you, by this rule, must adore all mankind.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
